snippet.title: Racist Posts That Landed Celebs In Hot Water
snippet.description:
In this day and age where social media is a big part of the culture as well as the frequent source of controversy, you have to be careful before posting anything online.

When you are a celebrity, you have to be extra careful because one wrong post and your career could go lights out. However, some stars just can’t help themselves and go trigger happy with their social media posts.

Then there are celebs who totally cross the line by posting racist content which would obviously land them in hot water. Who are these ignorant celebrities, and what racist content did they post? To find out, watch this video!

#Racist #Celebs #HotWater

Roseanne Barr | 0:00
Amber Heard | 1:25
Rihanna | 2:27
Chelsea Handler | 3:20
Israel Broussard | 4:17
